      "content": "the candles are all burned down to nothing... and so am i. he's gone, and the silence in this house is heavier than the stone of the abbey. it feels so much more natural to just... stop. to let the darkness take me rather than face another dawn without him. it would be so quiet, wouldn't it? just fading away like mist.",
