      "content": "it feels so much more honest than anything else. everyone tells me to \"hold on\" or \"stay strong\" but they don't understand how heavy it actually is. they act like there's something to wait for, but looking at the shadows in the corner of this room... it just feels like the weight is finally pulling me toward something better. something calm. you seem to understand that. you don't sound like they do.",
